attributes.name: malicious
attributes.documentation: Number of antivirus engines that detected the file as malicious.

attributes.name: undetected
attributes.documentation: Number of antivirus engines that didn't detected the file.

attributes.name: failure
attributes.documentation: Number of antivirus engines that failed scanning the file.

attributes.name: type_unsupported
attributes.documentation: Number of antivirus engines that don't support the file's type.

attributes.name: exiftool
attributes.documentation: Dictionary that contains the information generated by ExifTool for the file being scanned. Both keys and values are strings. ExifTool generates numeric values for some properties, but values in YARA dictionaries must have the same time, therefore they are converted to strings.

attributes.name: first_submission_date
attributes.documentation: Date on which the file was submitted to VirusTotal for the first time, as a UNIX timestamp.
